Today, at the representative office of the Kherson region in Moscow, a working meeting was held with Aleksey Valentinovich Gamaev, director of the autonomous non-profit organization Center for Social and Health Rehabilitation "Medsanbat" and Oleg Vladimirovich Yartsev, head of the executive committee of the regional public organization "Society of Disabled War Invalids in Afghanistan - Moscow Soldier's Home" .
The following issues were discussed:
- organization and delivery of medical humanitarian aid to the Kherson region;
- organization of rehabilitation and prosthetics for Kherson residents of the Northern Military District in the “Moscow House of Soldiers’ Heart”;
- combining the efforts of parallel educational structures in Moscow and Kherson in matters of military and social rehabilitation of disabled participants of the North Military District through obtaining the military specialty “UAV operator”;
- holding joint events in Moscow between the representative office and internationalist soldiers on the basis of the “Moscow House of Soldiers’ Heart”;
- assistance and media support from the representative office of "Medsanbat" and "Moscow House of Soldiers' Heart" in their activities in the Kherson region.

